text: Hockeyclub Oranje-Rood (), also known as HC Oranje-Rood or simply Oranje-Rood, is a Dutch field hockey club based in Eindhoven, North-Brabant. The club was founded on 1 July 2016 as a merger of Oranje Zwart and EMHC. In May 2019, the first women's team won the club its first prize by winning the Dutch national cup, the Gold Cup. ==Honours== ===Men=== Euro Hockey League * Runners-up (1): 2016–17 ===Women=== Gold Cup * Winners (1): 2018–19 ==Players== ===Current squad=== ====Women's squad==== Head coach: Stefan Duyf ====Men's squad==== Head coach: Robert van der Horst ==References== ==External links== * Official website Category:Sports clubs in Eindhoven Category:Dutch field hockey clubs Category:Field hockey clubs established in 2016 Category:2016 establishments in the Netherlands
